&lt;li&gt;Proven track record leading complex, cross-functional escalations and driving root cause elimination — not just resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong programming proficiency in one or more languages; ability to build tools, conduct peer code review, and contribute to Engineering R&amp;amp;D with a supportability lens&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High understanding of distributed service architecture across product specialty areas, including AI-powered component integration and failure modes&lt;/li&gt;
